description=Adds a probability-based item rarity system (Common, Uncommon, Rare, Epic, Legendary). ANY item can spawn with ANY rarity based on global probabilities (60% Common, 25% Uncommon, 10% Rare, 4% Epic, 1% Legendary). Higher rarity items spawn less frequently. Starlit Library is optional - install it to see detailed bonus information in tooltips.

